OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells on Monday with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain. Dry start Tuesday but becoming
OL,8,Fwindier as rain spreads east later.
OL,9,FWindy on Wednesday as rain clears to
OL,10,Fsunny spells and showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
